        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Why do I need PKCE?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "PKCE (Proof Key for Code Exchange) replaces the need for a static Client Secret in public applications (like SPAs and mobile apps) where secrets cannot be stored securely, preventing authorization code injection attacks."
        }
      }
    ]
  }
